data.description:
This corner lot house is located in the desirable neighborhood of The Ranches of Forest Ridge.  There is so much to do on 3.14 acres of land, including: a heated salt-water pool, newer hot tub that seats 6-8 people, chicken coop, dog run, green house and plenty of space to entertain. This is truly a retreat from the city life and a must-see for anyone wanting land or country life. 

Primary bedroom and a bedroom/office are on the main floor. The non-conforming bedroom in basement has a walk-in closet. Pool table in the basement comes with the house. The aquarium in the family room also stays. The refrigerator and stove were replaced in 2022. All appliances are staying with the house. The Seller is also leaving the riding lawn-mower.  Sellers repainted the interior in 2021. 

Open House this Saturday, November 11th, 10am until 3pm. Stop by and take a look at this great property!
